      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see, so it's just about things being held in memory because they're still being \"pointed to\" by something else. it's a bit frustrating though, it feels like there's something invisible constantly siphoning off my resources. how do i actually track down where these leaks are coming from? are there specific tools or ways to see exactly what's grabbing all that space?",
